'Young Paperboyz' is Mayor Boss and Della Ratta better known as simply Young
Paperboyz, Mayor Boss (born June 5, 1986) and Della Ratta (born October 27,
1987) is a Nigeria Hip/Hop, R&B & Pop group who are based in Ukraine. Young
Paperboyz derived there stage name from friends when they are growing up
back in 2007
